OOC: Does rampage have his whole spark again?

BIC: Mutate decided to talk his way out if he could.

Mutate: To be honest I haven't taken the Maximal's
side yet, but with Predicons like you around I'm real
close. I don't want to destroy you, but rest assured I
am quite capable.

OOC: Isn't it moding not to accept any damage?

--- robertdahl <rdahl@...> wrote:
> Megatron nimbly kept flying around, to keep face to
> face with Mutate,
> smoothly dodging left and right, waiting to try and
> crush this horrible
> creation.
>
----------------------------------------------------------------------
> "The darkness felt so cold, I was alone, and
> terrified. Ahhhh how I've
> missed those feelings." He then felt mutate's pain.
> "Ahhhh, an old
> friend, who is feeling pain. I must meet the one who
> iduced this.
> RAMPAGE, TERRORIZE." At the command, the ground tore
> opend, leaving the
> monster predacon to break free from the earth that
> was his grave since
> the Predacon's last stand against the Maximals. He
> looked around, and
> could see nothing, but could feel the spark he
> wanted. He leapt into the
> air, and converted into his tank mode, landing on
> the ground with a
> large thud, as he started to roll towards the new
> Maximal city.
>
